es out with no terminal result event, the run is reported as a timeout failure (existing behavior preserved).\n- [ ] AC-3: A warning is logged when a terminal result event is found after timeout.\n- [ ] AC-4: Unit tests cover both paths (result present, result absent) and edge cases (malformed JSON, multiple JSON lines).\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
